  "description": "This refrigerator was able to combine excellent capacity, performance and impressive functionality. The unit is equipped with a free space of 535 liters. A key feature of the model was the integration of a dispenser and an ice maker into the freezer door. The operation of the dispenser is autonomous, the Gorenje NRS 9182 VX refrigerator does not need to be connected to the water supply. The ice maker is capable of making both cubes and ice porridge. This is a bright representative of Side-by-side refrigeration units. Convenient hinged doors provide easy access to all storage shelves and drawers. The model workspace uses the concept of XtraSpace. Loading and unloading products is now faster and safer than ever. LedLight illumination will allow you to immediately find what you are looking for. The role of the cooling system is performed by MultiFlow 360° technology. With this option, each shelf and each drawer is individually cooled. The refrigeration unit uses an inverter compressor. This is a quiet and powerful power plant that can create the perfect microclimate for storing the entire list of products without any hassle.",
